	<p>First we need some information that can possibly help us to make sense of the results after 
	the experiment. If you don't know an answer exactly, a rough estimate will suffice.</p>
	<form action="exp/$exp.id/intro.html" method="post" autocomplete="off">
		<!-- role -->
		<fieldset>
			<p>What is your main role?</p>
			<input type="radio" name="role" id="role_0" value="programmer" required="true"><label for="role_0">Programmer / Software Developer</label><br/>
			<input type="radio" name="role" id="role_1" value="tester" required="true"><label for="role_1">Tester</label><br/>
			<input type="radio" name="role" id="role_2" value="analyst" required="true"><label for="role_2">Analyst</label><br/>
			<input type="radio" name="role" id="role_3" value="architect" required="true"><label for="role_3">Software Architect</label><br/>
			<input type="radio" name="role" id="role_4" value="operations" required="true"><label for="role_4">IT Operations</label><br/>
			<input type="radio" name="role" id="role_5" value="manager" required="true"><label for="role_5">Manager</label><br/>
